type coercion 형 변환

Under what circumstance is it acceptable to use implicit type coercion?


(Example)
let num1 = 9 * "3";
console.log(num1); // 27 (a number)
let num2 = 9 + "3";
console.log(num2); // "93" (a string)


false == ""; // true
false == "0"; // true
"" == "0"; // false
[0] == 0; // true
